4,11,"Electronics Retail Database","Electronics Retail Database is a comprehensive database for a small chain of electronics stores. The goal is to keep track of inventory, keep track of product locations, record transactions and online orders, keep shipping information, and record employee information. This database will be more efficient and easier to interact with than an incredibly large excel file. Users will easily be able to check stock or product location. Employees will be able to update the inventory information and view online orders. Administrators will be able to manage and update all information.","20XX-04-19 04:05:00"
